title: The Big Suey: Don't Do It
description:
Stugotz predictably doesn't want us to write off Tom Brady after the Bucs scored 3 points against Carolina, Witty is concerned for Derrick Henry after he picked up 30 more carries, Tony has a provocative Giants question, Billy hates the Phillies, and Dan is tired of watching backup quarterbacks. It's the week 7 NFL postgame show.
